stimulusHtml: Set up, but do not integrate, an integral expression in terms of a single variable for the volume of the solid generated when R is revolved about the y-axis.

features.html: Let R be the region in the first quadrant enclosed by the graph of y = 6 x + 4 MathType@MTEF@5@5@@3B62@ , the line y = 2x , and the y-axis.
